text: Toshihiko Sasano (born 2 November 1911, date of death unknown) was a Japanese gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1932 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Japanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 1932 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
